        <sponsor name-id="S288">Ms. Murkowski</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="S332">Mr. Franken</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S311">Ms. Klobuchar</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S221">Mrs. Feinstein</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S319">Mr. Begich</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S316">Mr. Whitehouse</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S131">Mr. Levin</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S295">Mr. Pryor</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSVA00">Committee on Veterans' Affairs</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
